WEBVTT

00:00.020 --> 00:01.626
Previously on "Graves"...

00:01.667 --> 00:03.666
I'm so glad we found each other, Olivia.

00:03.667 --> 00:06.666
Olivia, stop! Come on, let me ex...

00:06.667 --> 00:10.666
I just want to be anyone
else for one fucking moment.

00:10.667 --> 00:12.256
The Rockefellers want a mediation.

00:12.257 --> 00:14.045
What haven't you told us, honey?

00:14.046 --> 00:16.666
Mrs. Graves, you have a son

00:16.667 --> 00:18.666
- with unsolved issues of his past.
- This one's for you.

00:18.667 --> 00:21.666
This is Martin
Treadwell's first release request

00:21.667 --> 00:23.666
since his attempt
on the president's life.

00:23.667 --> 00:26.666
Why would I worry? It's
not like this hasn't stuck to me.

00:26.667 --> 00:28.204
Sammy, I like you.

00:28.205 --> 00:29.666
Are you okay?

00:29.667 --> 00:31.667
Yeah.

00:39.073 --> 00:41.929
This is all new territory for me.

00:42.968 --> 00:44.667
Brand-new.

00:47.667 --> 00:49.666
What?

00:50.688 --> 00:54.152
Nothing.

00:54.667 --> 00:55.953
I just...

00:57.667 --> 00:59.666
I like the way you look at me.

00:59.667 --> 01:02.667
It's like you found
a unicorn or something.

01:06.667 --> 01:08.666
- Isaiah.
- Oh, shit!

01:08.667 --> 01:11.666
- Kitchen, now.
- I'll sneak out.

01:11.667 --> 01:13.667
- Good idea.
- Okay.

